{"tid":1631463,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"叫翻自衛反擊 唔好再叫私了","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:35:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T01:04:59.000Z","uid":137265,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"255459cb2874168325124c602f3fac0365e6c840","tid":1631463,"uid":137265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:35:20.000Z","msg":"唔只係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>對外</strong></span></span>宣傳，仲係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>對內</strong></span></span>宣傳<br />\n自衛反擊有前設，係為左保障自身安全反制對方，亦係建基於武力對等嘅情況之下<br />\n私了冇，大事小事皆可私了，觸發條件太低<br />\n情緒一激動就好易過火，而且道德底線比自衛反擊低好多<br />\n<br />\n正如nazi同警察叫市民做曱甴一樣<br />\n大家唔好低估文字影響意識嘅威力<br />\n係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">自衛反擊</span></strong></span>，唔係私了<br />\n希望手足每一次都係為人身安全行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好單純為左發洩不忿<br />\n<br />\n唔好再講咩獅鳥神獸，未MK夠咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EjR8fR8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEjR8fR8.jpg&h=3094aaf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">明白前線手足真係好大壓力<br />\n呢排又開槍又的士恐襲<br />\n講緊一個禮拜都未夠就發生曬<br />\n但出手前都停一停諗一諗啦<br />\n最後裝修四色啊</span></span>"},{"pid":"468dc3b427ed8a567df91b057fefd2558ad9973e","tid":1631463,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:35:45.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：文宣洗地開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e3678bf7e08ff6e4946b0fc1b4e85188c84ba105","tid":1631463,"uid":137265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:35:50.000Z","msg":"4連"},{"pid":"d0ffece916c90f2c081b6d605258807ccaaa0fd4","tid":1631463,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:35:54.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"36d2f2220173a85b73b63bd7f3b51c6484c8eea7","tid":1631463,"uid":137265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:36:02.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"3dd234f3a02e4f5f8b80adf904d192cf1948e45e","tid":1631463,"uid":137265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:36:24.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"591b81e92ec2752e2cdc6557af4b2e0e2629a95e","tid":1631463,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:36:30.000Z","msg":"強烈建議和武合一令星期二香城真正變死城<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631356\" data-auto-link targ